fields.title: Image from kitchen tag
fields.caption: I can’t wait to make some memories here.
fields.description: Every house or home should have a kitchen for convenience. It is a room you frequently use to prepare meals for either you or the entire family.A kitchen is mainly located on the first floor, and it is mostly near the dining area.

fields.title: Image from dining tag
fields.caption: Hey, home! Nice to meet you.
fields.description: Most people prefer having a dining room in an area adjacent to the kitchen.Some dining rooms are more extensive, while others are small, depending on the number of people living in the house and the available space.Some prefer having a long narrow ornate room with long tables. Mostly a dining room will have tables and chairs.

fields.description: A bedroom is one of the essential rooms in a house.
